title: Pets Welcome, Intrusion Alarms, Spacious closets
posting_body: ['YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', 'Carrington Park at Gulf Pointe boasts one of the most prominent locations on the outer loop, with great proximity to access I-45 and Beltway 8.', 'The location at our Houston area apartments allows you to enjoy unmatched convenience to Downtown, NASA’s Johnson Space Center, Houston’s Hobby Airport, and the most elite shopping and dining that Houston has to offer.', ' Our Apartments in Houston, TX have more than just location to offer.', 'Take a look at our property amenities including a resort-style pool with Wi-Fi, gourmet grilling areas, a billiards room and more.', 'Contact us to find out how to make Carrington Park at Gulf Pointe the place you will be proud to call home!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Enjoy our Partnership with Comcast Cable', 'Poolside Gourmet Grilling Areas', 'Pets Welcome', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Auto Detailing Bay', 'Billiards Room', 'Ceiling Fans in Living Room & Master Bedroom', "Chef's Kitchen", 'Attached Garages with Individual Driveway and Private Entry', 'Full Size Washer & Dryer', 'In Each Apartment Home', 'Strength and Cardio Center', 'Hardwood Plank Flooring', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
